Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,2 years have passed since the Paramount War.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew returned to Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and on their way to the New World, they reached Fishman Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and the others find themselves caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro and the others facing Hody and the New Fishman Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...tried to escape after the tides turned against them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but were caught by Hody whose strength was multiplied tremendously
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by taking the Energy Steroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Luffy and the others finally got to the Sea Forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is responsible for setting Arlong loose into the East Blue was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...me!
