Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep going, there'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,King Neptune...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look back! Think about what the King did for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the Bubbly Coral!
