Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So few soldiers made it out even after we left the King there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop moaning! It was the King's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, this is not a retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We will exterminate the pirates in the palace and rescue the King at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we need to communicate with Prince Fukaboshi and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in touch with the Princes A.S.A.P. and reorganize the forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and let's go back to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
