Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:56.57,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Daruma
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.63,0:06:56.57,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Daruma
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means they're our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.94,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}In Front of the Fish Cultural Center
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.94,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}In Front of the Fish Cultural Center
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.94,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,In front of the Fish Cultural Center in the southeast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.95,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa! It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:15.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\pos(840.5,715)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Hyouzou
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.38,0:07:15.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\pos(840.5,715)\4a&HFF&}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Hyouzou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.69,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,It's either step on this image or flee from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.89,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it! If somebody refused to do either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've been told to slice 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.18,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Marine Shopping Mall
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.18,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Marine Shopping Mall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.18,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,At the Marine Shopping Mall in the east...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Leave the country"? Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place on the seafloor that has light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't live in the humans' world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see how heartlessly the humans discriminate against others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way that humans and Fishmen can get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You must submit to King Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.25,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,We will reign over humans and change history!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\pos(1407,715)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Zeo
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.25,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\pos(1407,715)\4a&HFF&}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Zeo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:18.15,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Waterwheel Town
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.31,0:08:18.15,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Waterwheel Town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.15,DefaultLow2,,0,0,0,,At Waterwheel Town in the north...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--Now, you're next. --It's gonna be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.83,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Dosun
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.83,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord0\4a&HFF&}New Fishman Pirates, Officer Dosun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:33.83,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pummel those who won't step on it-dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Fukaboshi! Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you are doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you make people of this country tread on the image of my late mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.96,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Coral Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.96,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Coral Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.96,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,At Coral Hill, after Luffy and the others left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--What should we do?! --We let Vander Decken get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we couldn't stop the Straw Hats from taking Princess Shirahoshi away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Princess said that she'd be back by dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! They made her say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A group from the Fishman District is rampaging all over the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?! --What's going on on the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid girls are going missing all around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If they sell the Princess to the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it seems like another Mermaid girl went missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I took her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, I just saw something great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A big size Mermaid-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A human-sized Mermaid is worth 70 million
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so if I can catch a Mermaid who is 7 or 8 times bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and sell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a bundle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:29.25,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Sea Forest
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.74,0:10:29.25,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.4\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Sea Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.68,DefaultLow2,,0,0,0,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they got the King but they can't really take his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And I will save the King at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I will be counting on you, Boss-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me talk to Luffy-kun and the others for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Leave it there, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're having a serious conversation so stop acting like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Nami-san, even when you're so severe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-chin hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Jinbe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You set Arlong loose into the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When Luffy and I first heard the name Jinbe of the Seven Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what Yosaku told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for joining the Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe set loose a terrible man into the East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Was that what he said? --I bet you don't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Yosaku is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When I read that you were with Jinbe 2 years ago in the newspaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it raised so many questions in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I thought Jinbe was the key figure who was pulling Arlong's strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna make excuses, I'll listen. But you better watch what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, this beautiful navigator - Nami-san here had her home island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...taken over by Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's been through hell because of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on what you have to say, I might not forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--Jinbe-san! --Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds are gonna open up again! Don't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! We gave her so much pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...that we can't heal no matter how much we apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna use my navigation skills to travel to all the world’s oceans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I’m gonna make a world map of everything I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So your map of this island is your first step toward your dream, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fill-in mother for you two, Nami and Nojiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are my dear family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in excellent spirits, pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As of this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,this village - no, this island - is now under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,100,000 berries per adult. 50,000 berries per kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who can’t pay... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:15:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can’t say I don’t have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even... if it costs me my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe we’re not related by blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we’re a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be their parent, even if it’s only in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re... my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Die with your pathetic love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nojiko! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--A sea chart? --No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew that! It's important to me! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You drew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--Give it back! --Nami! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s an invaluable asset! Bring her with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--Right! --No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no food for humans! Shut up and keep drawing maps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather up 100 million berries and bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do so and I’ll let the village go and give you freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief! She stole our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's a kid! --Who cares! Shoot her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:17:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,70 million more... 70 million more to free the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! It seems like you have nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, my dear navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you had a terrible experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Don't distance yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It would never make me change the way I feel about Arlong,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but until I went to Sabaody Archipelago 2 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew that such tough Fishmen were persecuted by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When Camie was kidnapped and I was going after her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabaody Park in front of me looked exactly like Arlong Park that Arlong built!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We were yearning for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just saying this to make you forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami! Arlong-san really didn't like humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He hated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But ever since we were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we yearned for the world that humans live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, Arlong-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we hurt so many humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi, don't push yourself! I'm gonna prepare some medicine so lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Fishmen and Merfolk were considered mere fish a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But 200 years ago, the Ryugu Kingdom became a member country of the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They established friendly relations with humans
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the king was allowed to participate in the World Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that, humans kept disliking Fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst time that I experienced was the beginning of the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I vividly remember the fear of seeing human pirates running wild on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get it off of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island was taken over by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the late, good-old Whitebeard saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He claimed Fishman Island as his own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and peace returned to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it didn't stop humans from disliking Fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you people saw it at Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The funny thing is those who seize power tend to be more afraid of change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the Government bridged the gap between Fishmen and humans
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,those who held the real power ended up being much more bigoted than all the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The relationship between Fishmen and humans remained the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, two people rose up on Fishman Island, to change our hopeless history.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One was Queen Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept trying to tell the islanders to live in harmony with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She was Princess Shirahoshi's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other is the hero who freed the slaves - Fisher Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something Tiger... I heard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling for parting ways with humans, he broke an unspoken rule
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and invaded the Holy Land of Mary Geoise by himself and freed the slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, he formed the Sun Pirates with the Fishmen who were slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Me, Arlong, and Hachi joined the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...crew of the Sun Pirates, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, having the "Fishman Pirates" who went against the Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...made it harder for Queen Otohime to establish good relations with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime was trying to weather great hardships and change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fisher Tiger threw his future away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to save the slaves of his race who were suffering at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can say which one was right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They fought for the future of Fishmen and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They were two monumental figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was their hidden angst?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime tried to guide the Ryugu Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,toward a future where humans and Fishmen could live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There was also Fisher Tiger, a hero who rescued Fishmen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from enslavement by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fates intertwined as they imagined a new future for Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and an incident that shaped history occurred!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Hero Who Freed the Slaves\NTiger the Adventurer"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
